### Lessons API
### Base URL: /api/v1/lessons/

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### Get all published lessons
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/ HTTP/1.1

### Get lesson by UUID
# Replace with actual UUIDs from the list response
@lessonUuid = 19e9abaa-f851-4db4-9380-7a307553dec1

GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonUuid}}/ HTTP/1.1

### Get lesson with course context (breadcrumbs)
# course param is optional — returns course: {uuid, title} or course: null
@courseUuid = ab704909-8661-4f1b-8d90-0ee430323c4d

GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonUuid}}/?course={{courseUuid}} HTTP/1.1

### Get non-existent lesson (expects 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/00000000-0000-0000-0000-111111111111/ HTTP/1.1
